OL,4,CPlans to crack down on online rip-offs
OL,5,Cunveiled
OL,6, A plan to crack down on online rip-offs
OL,7, including making it illegal for people
OL,8, to write or host fake reviews has been
OL,9, outlined by the government.
OL,11,FThe proposals would see prepayment
OL,12,Fschemes such as Christmas savings clubs
OL,13,Fhave to safeguard customers' money.
OL,15,FBusinesses offering subscriptions would
OL,16,Falso be required to make clear exactly
OL,17,Fwhat consumers are signing up for and
OL,18,Fallow them to cancel easily.
OL,20,FConsumer champion Which? said the plans
OL,21,Fshould be "swiftly implemented".
